// Area Chart ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã…Â¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â using react-native-svg
function AreaChart({ data }: { data: { label: string; value: number }[] }) {
    if (!data || data.length === 0) return null;
    const maxVal = Math.max(...data.map(d => d.value), 100);
    const CHART_HEIGHT = 120;
    const CHART_WIDTH = 300; // rough width, responsive SVG will scale it
    const PADDING_TOP = 20;
    const PADDING_BOTTOM = 25;
    const PADDING_X = 15;
    const innerHeight = CHART_HEIGHT - PADDING_TOP - PADDING_BOTTOM;
    const innerWidth = CHART_WIDTH - PADDING_X * 2;

    const dx = innerWidth / Math.max(1, data.length - 1);

    // Generate points
    const points = data.map((d, i) => {
        const x = PADDING_X + i * dx;
        const y = PADDING_TOP + innerHeight - (d.value / maxVal) * innerHeight;
        return { x, y, value: d.value, label: d.label };
    });

    const pathD = points.map((p, i) => (i === 0 ? `M ${p.x},${p.y}` : `L ${p.x},${p.y}`)).join(' ');
    // Close path for area
    const areaD = `${pathD} L ${points[points.length - 1].x},${CHART_HEIGHT - PADDING_BOTTOM} L ${points[0].x},${CHART_HEIGHT - PADDING_BOTTOM} Z`;

    return (
        <View style={{ height: CHART_HEIGHT, width: '100%', paddingHorizontal: 4 }}>
            <Svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox={`0 0 ${CHART_WIDTH} ${CHART_HEIGHT}`}>
                <Defs>
                    <LinearGradient id="grad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                        <Stop offset="0" stopColor="#EAB308" stopOpacity="0.4" />
                        <Stop offset="1" stopColor="#EAB308" stopOpacity="0.0" />
                    </LinearGradient>
                </Defs>

                {/* Horizontal grid lines */}
                {[0, 0.5, 1].map((pct, i) => (
                    <Line
                        key={i}
                        x1={PADDING_X}
                        y1={PADDING_TOP + innerHeight * pct}
                        x2={CHART_WIDTH - PADDING_X}
                        y2={PADDING_TOP + innerHeight * pct}
                        stroke="#E5E7EB"
                        strokeWidth="1"
                    />
                ))}

                {/* Vertical grid lines */}
                {points.map((p, i) => (
                    <Line
                        key={`v-${i}`}
                        x1={p.x}
                        y1={PADDING_TOP}
                        x2={p.x}
                        y2={CHART_HEIGHT - PADDING_BOTTOM}
                        stroke="#E5E7EB"
                        strokeWidth="1"
                    />
                ))}

                <Path d={areaD} fill="url(#grad)" />
                <Path d={pathD} fill="none" stroke="#EAB308" strokeWidth="2" />

                {points.map((p, i) => (
                    <React.Fragment key={i}>
                        <SvgCircle cx={p.x} cy={p.y} r="3" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#EAB308" strokeWidth="2" />
                        <SvgText
                            x={p.x}
                            y={p.y - 8}
                            fontSize="8"
                            fill="#6B7280"
                            textAnchor="middle"
                        >
                            {p.value > 0 ? (p.value >= 1000000 ? `${(p.value / 1000000).toFixed(1)}jt` : `${Math.round(p.value / 1000)}k`) : ''}
                        </SvgText>
                        <SvgText
                            x={p.x}
                            y={CHART_HEIGHT - 10}
                            fontSize="9"
                            fill="#6B7280"
                            textAnchor="middle"
                        >
                            {p.label}
                        </SvgText>
                    </React.Fragment>
                ))}
            </Svg>
        </View>
    );
}

// Simple Horizontal Bar Chart
function SimpleBarChart({ data }: { data: { label: string; value: number }[] }) {
    if (!data || data.length === 0) return null;
    const maxVal = Math.max(...data.map(d => d.value), 1);
    return (
        <View style={tw`mt-2`}>
            {data.map((item, idx) => (
                <View key={idx} style={tw`mb-3`}>
                    <View style={tw`flex-row justify-between mb-1`}>
                        <Text style={tw`text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 font-bold`}>{item.label}</Text>
                        <Text style={tw`text-xs text-blue-600 font-black`}>{formatRp(item.value)}</Text>
                    </View>
                    <View style={tw`h-6 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-full overflow-hidden`}>
                        <View
                            style={[
                                tw`h-full bg-blue-500 rounded-full`,
                                { width: `${Math.max(2, (item.value / maxVal) * 100)}%` }
                            ]}
                        />
                    </View>
                </View>
            ))}
        </View>
    );
}

